snippet.title: UNDERTALE PlayStation 4, PS Vita E3 2017 Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PS4 and PS Vita August 15, 2017!

For more info, visit: http://www.undertale.com

Trailer by Everdraed + Fangamer
3D by Chelsea Saunders
VO by Kyle Hebert
